The article discusses President Donald J. Trump's efforts to improve support and healthcare for veterans in the United States. It highlights the years of scandal that have plagued the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) and emphasizes the need for accountability and reform. The President is focused on modernizing and expanding choice within the VA, aiming to provide the best healthcare possible for veterans. Additionally, he is taking action to create more opportunities for veterans after they leave military service and working to ensure that veterans are properly recognized for their service and sacrifice.